{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDc3NjA1NTk4", "number": 1456, "title": "HIVE-24106: Abort polling on the operation state when the current thr\u2026", "bodyText": "\u2026ead is interrupted\n\nWhat changes were proposed in this pull request?\nAbort polling on the operation state when the current thread is interrupted\n\nWhy are the changes needed?\nIf running HiveStatement asynchronously as a task like in a thread or future,  if we interrupt the task,  the HiveStatement would continue to poll on the operation state until finish. It's may better to provide a way to abort the executing in such case.\n\nDoes this PR introduce any user-facing change?\nNo\n\nHow was this patch tested?\nLocal machine", "createdAt": "2020-09-02T06:33:30Z", "url": "https://github.com/apache/hive/pull/1456", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "6392c0e7f16f0f767aa8c1b70eafa672c0b7865f"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-10-14T07:51:44Z", "author": {"login": "dengzhhu653"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 5, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdE1_ALgH2gAyNDc3NjA1NTk4OmYyNWRjYzY4YTI1NTUwMTczYzJkNjUzZDkzNzQzNGY3ZDE4NGU1NTg=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdSYXs-gFqTUwODA4MTU1Ng==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "f25dcc68a25550173c2d653d937434f7d184e558", "author": {"user": {"login": "dengzhhu653", "name": "dengzh"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/hive/commit/f25dcc68a25550173c2d653d937434f7d184e558", "committedDate": "2020-09-02T06:26:43Z", "message": "HIVE-24106: Abort polling on the operation state when the current thread is interrupted"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTA1NDcwNDcy", "url": "https://github.com/apache/hive/pull/1456#pullrequestreview-505470472", "createdAt": "2020-10-09T08:34:11Z", "commit": {"oid": "f25dcc68a25550173c2d653d937434f7d184e558"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1,